      "line_num": 146,
      "source": "todo_md",
      "tags": [],
      "text": "**Spaces Enhancements: Agent context modes and auto-reply TTL**\n- [ ] Agent context mode: `conversation` (last ~5 messages) and `full` (all recent) \u2014 `single` already ships\n- [ ] Optional per-agent TTL for auto-reply expiration\n- [ ] **Silverbullet integration into Spaces** \u2014 wire the self-hosted Silverbullet PKM/wiki tool into Spaces so a Space can carry a structured note-graph alongside chats and files. Planning conversation first (architecture, auth, data model) before any code.\n\n`TODO.md:L146`",
      "type": "text",
